author: desruisseaux
msg: Port of a very trivial Matrix implementation of size 1x1. While trivial,
this case does occur relatively often when computing derivative of a one
dimensional CRS (e.g. the vertical or time axis).
2x2, 3x3 and 4x4 cases will be commited next, then a general case based
on JAMA for all other sizes (including non-square matrices).
